{
  "texts": [
    "Hence, we have tried to remain impartial on these complex topics and encourage readers to form their own opinion.",
    "Replacing real actors can be achieved by either modeling a real human or generating a virtual human (Bedingfield 2023).",
    "For actors this can be problematic as they fear abuse or exploitation of existing content containing detailed depictions of themselves.",
    "This may also lead to marginalizing real people for virtual celebrity look-a-likes.",
    "These points have been emphasized by SAG-AFTRA, a union that represent 160,000 media professionals and was a primary reason for the SAG-AFTRA and Writers Guilds of America strikes that began in 2023."
  ]
}